FuncDef: The unload ai-service model-file command uninstalls a model file imported into the embedded AI system. The unload ai-service model-file command uninstalls a model file imported into the embedded AI system.

ParaDef.Info:
Specifies the name of a model package file.
The value is a string of 1 to 63 case-sensitive characters, spaces not supported.

ExtraInfo: You can run this command to uninstall the model file imported to the embedded AI system.
